description: Try our easy to follow Chicken Tacos recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
keywords: Taco,Seafood free,Low salt,Gluten free,Tree nut free,Egg free,Low sugar,Sesame free,High protein,High fibre,Soy free,Wheat free,Tomato,Chicken,Avocado,Peanut free
name: Chicken Tacos Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Cook whole chicken as per packet instructions. Remove meat and discard bones. Shred meat.
Heat Taco Shells following packet instructions.
Fill with shredded lettuce, sliced tomatoes, shredded carrot, roughly mashed avocado.

Top with shredded chicken, Mild Salsa and 1 cup grated cheese. Did you know? Some Mexicans eat tacos for breakfast filled with fresh fruit and vegetables. Make your own Aussie version filled with baked beans or egg, ham and cheese.
